{"tid":1135622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係近年香港馬圈最黑暗既一日，馬會高層董事我屌晒你地老母你地全部不得好死","createTime":"2019-05-02T12:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T07:39:54.000Z","uid":40938,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8291d100fd6dbcfdca64a896998cb62a2518f46f","tid":1135622,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"大清賴維銘92年開始做騎師，到依家27年，幫你馬會騎左廿幾年馬，今時今日得返咁既待遇，真係冇人會嚥得下呢啖氣。<br />\n唔講其他野住，淨係廿幾年幫你馬會騎盡外國大騎師唔騎既閪馬，冇功都有勞掛？點解華人受傷比鬼佬多？唔係因為華人特別屎，係因為佢地騎啲馬特別閪呀！拎條命幫你打工，你班董事咁對人唔驚有報應？<br />\n講返今次放頭，鬼佬同類甚至咁閪既事多不勝數，我係咁易cap俾大家睇下:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「精算齊同」2月13日由莫雷拉執韁出戰谷草1650米賽事，在頭兩段比標準時間快0.14秒底下，仍然力策這匹從來未曾放過頭的五歲馬，試圖趕過「活力勇士」放頭，導致第三段步速比快0.92秒，最後潰敗得第十名。<br />\n<br />\n翌仗改配何澤堯留後卻輕鬆取勝，更印證該仗騎師發揮大有問題，事後莫雷拉卻只被查詢馬匹表現。<br />\n<br />\n在剛過去的女皇盃當中，田泰安策騎「馬克羅斯」放頭，頭四段居然比標準時間快3.24秒，參考競賽小組昨日（30日）判詞，可以說「馬匹比標準分段時間快至少19個馬位」，賽後卻未見競賽事件報告有任何一字提及此事。</span><br />\n<br />\n其他更多更多鬼佬仆街野大家馬迷看在眼內，董事就問都唔問。今次大清唔再玩，係有骨氣，但唔代表你地董事可以善終。<br />\n<br />\n諗起大清今季開鑼贏馬，笑得幾燦爛，點估到季尾都完唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipH8NDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipH8NDx.png&h=68223441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真心respect 大師兄賴維銘"},{"pid":"d6687eed24c248bdb14f6bc534c841eacf79e0f1","tid":1135622,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"大大件潘頓冇人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5817b6589b8f033ac44dc7f1b3abd5bce9a1b06","tid":1135622,"uid":40938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSdsiVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSdsiVk.png&h=b2299b93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"251b48f9fa79a8de671cfde57ce00d9fafc3cfc6","tid":1135622,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"從來都係鬼佬馬會"},{"pid":"118e16931687f506dfa0c227b7fbb0f98531ae63","tid":1135622,"uid":53672,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"班廢老成日話失地中國人咩咩咩，又話我地廢青崇洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢單明恰華人 叫佢地罷賭抗議唔知有咩反應呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43af8bb6b7a8aeec334193093abe888e2f7c8d1f","tid":1135622,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"仲有利敬國拍馬頭呢"},{"pid":"f67f891540e3794014ffa9b99ef708164a2e1ec5","tid":1135622,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"廢潘幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738615a091b54e1e6289d01d7b8c5a3668dff787","tid":1135622,"uid":179606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"贏馬神器1600m 試過快標準時間翻到黎<br />\n跑1分34秒幾<br />\n配賴仔輕磅梗係搶放搏走甩"},{"pid":"7ca330c41ef187dff0c9a43331952dda5d04d563","tid":1135622,"uid":31542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"狗會不嬲都咁黑暗嫁啦 賭撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe138bc45b80cb8ff67fa1a3c7059d441d829585","tid":1135622,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca330c41ef187dff0c9a43331952dda5d04d563","tid":1135622,"uid":31542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"狗會不嬲都咁黑暗嫁啦 賭撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有喺度咒下佢地"},{"pid":"b19b7aa2a16d4ec286720e958e14f2c689e259ad","tid":1135622,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02